name: Miss M
description:
Miss M is part of an alphanumeric universe, each and everyone with its own charisma and personality. 
She is positive, energetic, and unaffected by today society regulations, she is powerful, and unbreakable, 
Miss M storyline begins today, and only the future knows what's next for her. Follow this series to uncover all characters and members of this unique society.

Illustrated on Photoshop October 2020.
